\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Oh yes, I used to get presents, but - not presents }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4070586\charrsid5840505 as }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 they are today you know, they used to - bring a bag of sweets perhaps and -
