\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did you play any games on Sunday, did your parents think it wrong to work or play on a Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Oh we always kept Sunday very select and very nice, we - there was no games played. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did your parents attend a place of worship, you all went to All Saints didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 How often did you go, you all went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Not on a morning - Sunday morning mother and dad didn't go but - I used to go and then - of course -
