\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 How many of those were you particularly friendly with?
