\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 I went to the Mother's Union, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did you go with anyone or did you just go by yourself?
