Often at the stores, the Co-operative stores you know when I used to go shopping. We used to go on a Thursday night and I used to meet quite a few.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did you and your husband share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 
No, not particular, I had me own and - and - he - if there was husband and wife and they went to church well of course - we were friendly but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did your husband have friends of his own, he would have singing friends wouldn't he?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 He had had his singing, yes. Then he was in the quarter you know and -
