\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 The one with the goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes, she was a great friend of m
ine. And still is. Yes. If she's - yes. She lives at Harrowgate Hill, and then there was another one as well, that used to - a sister-in-law, we were all very friendly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Were friends ever invited into the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 How often did you have friends in when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Well we used to take turns - on a Sunday night coming from church we used to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 You carried on the same system as your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes, yes. They used to come and we had musical evenings and - we used to have quite a nice time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 You said your husband was very good company didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 He was, he was a real - life and soul of a party. He was very jolly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did you ever have your friends in for anything to eat and drink during the week as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No. No, we didn't have - just a - unless anyone dropped in and - they just had a cup of tea or coffee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Would you say that the friends invited in were your husband's friends or friends that you both shared?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Well friends that we both shared.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 And sometimes friends called in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes. Often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Would that be any time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Oh yes, they used to come on a night if they'd been out for a walk and - just used to come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did your neighbours pop in any time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 You often went out to visit friends or neighbours didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 What did you do when you got together with friend or neighbours, obviously you had music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes. And used to have parties. And used to play games and - oh yes, we used to enjoy ourselves in the home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Was your home rented or did you own it when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 It was rented.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did you see anything of the landlord at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes, I often used to see him. He'd come once a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 How did you feel about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Oh he was a grand - man. Yes. It was a lovely house and we used to pay - six shillings a week all in. Yes, everything, the water 
rate and - and it was - beautiful little house. Venetian blinds and - and those things I dread - oh I hated. Specially when it came to cleaning time because - they aren't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4070586\charrsid5840505 Venetian}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505  blinds then that they are today. Wood you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 How did you clean them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 
Well you used to wash them and then varnish them and there was - they were taped, and I used to have to do the tapes over with - yellow ochre they called it, it was brown stuff, and I used to do them over and I thought I'd got half cleaned when I'd 
got those done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 In the district where you lived who were considered the most important people?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 The bank manager. Yes. And the schoolmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did you come into contact with them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Why do you think they were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 
Well they always though themselves a little bit better I think than anyone else. Whether they did although I don't know, but - we always thought they were. Perhaps it was the position.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 When you were married and living in Pearl Street, did the shopkeepers have any special friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 
No. We used to have - where I lived there was shop at each corner of the street and I used to go there and - I was registered with them and - oh, they were always very kind to me. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Were they friendly with the people all round your area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 And the clergyman used to come to your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 So he was friendly with you as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did the teachers have any particular friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No, I can't say - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Or the farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No. Just our own relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Who did the employers mix with when you were married in Shildon during the war? Do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 What sort of people would you say went to church then, when you were married?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Well just ordinary people, same as ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 And to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Where you lived did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No, we were all working people and we just seemed to - be sociable and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Do you think that one group felt itself more superior than the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No. No, we were all - on a level.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Were some families thought of as rough and some as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No. Some - there was - one family that had three rough boys, but - father and mother were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 No. No, just some of these quick rich people. They lose their heads.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 You think they go up in the world too quick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Did you ever have a struggle to make ends meet when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Well - working - my husband was working hard and we used to try and get things together and we did very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Was your husband ever ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Yes, he was very ill - with - he was off work about three months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15097456 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 What was the matter with him then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10968034 MC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8333860\charrsid5840505 Sciatica. And when he got -
\par }}